On this day in 1999: Arsenal completed the signing of 22-year-old Juventus winger Thierry Henry for a fee of around &pound;11m. #afc<br />
<br />
Wenger after signing Henry in 1999: &quot;Thierry has pace, power &amp; great dribbling. I would like to move him to the centre as the main striker.&quot;
